data.title: Was the Gurkani empire at the time of Shah Jahan more powerful than the Ottoman Empire under Sultan Murad IV?
data.meta_description:
Answer: No. I would say that the Ottoman Empire during the reign of Sultan Murad IV (1623 – 1640) was more powerful than the Timurid/Gurkani/Mughal Empire during the reign of Shah Jahan (1628 – 1658).
